《'''公报'''》（{{lang-en|''The Gazette''}}），中文全称《'''美国国会图书馆公报'''<ref name="Walker沃克1988">{{cite book|author1=David M. Walker|author2=沃克|title=牛津法律大辞典|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-LkUAQAAMAAJ|year=1988|publisher=[[光明日报出版社|光明日报出版社]]|pages=368-|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929065408/https://books.google.com/books?id=-LkUAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>》（{{lang|en|''The Library of Congress Gazette''}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lawyer.get.com.tw/Dic/DictionaryDetail.aspx?iDT=53989|title=政府公报|accessdate=2020-07-03|publisher=lawyer.get.com.tw|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703135226/http://lawyer.get.com.tw/Dic/DictionaryDetail.aspx?iDT=53989|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是一份由[[美国国会图书馆|美国国会图书馆]]出版发行的[[报纸|报纸]]<ref name="NiteckiKendrick2001">{{cite book|author1=Danuta A. Nitecki|author2=Curtis L. Kendrick|title=Library Off-site Shelving: Guide for High-density Facilities|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=v2aD9piTIFoC&pg=PA57|year=2001|publisher=Libraries Unlimited|isbn=978-1-56308-885-8|pages=57–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715174301/https://books.google.com/books?id=v2aD9piTIFoC&pg=PA57|dead-url=no}}</ref>，创刊于1990年4月6日，主要面向[[国会图书馆_(美国)|国会图书馆]]的工作人员。该报现任[[主编|主编]]（Executive Editor）是艾普若·斯莱顿（April Slayton），出版编辑（Publications Editor）是[[马克·哈特塞尔|马克·哈特塞尔]]（Mark Hartsell）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.loc.gov/static/portals/about/pandemic-information/documents/gazette/24_Gazette_061920_web.pdf|title=Weekly Gazette, June 19 issue - Library of Congress|date=2020-06-19|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|accessdate=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703170314/https://www.loc.gov/static/portals/about/pandemic-information/documents/gazette/24_Gazette_061920_web.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在时任[[国会图书馆_(美国)|国会图书馆]][[馆长|馆长]][[詹姆士·哈德利·比林顿|詹姆士·哈德利·比林顿]]（James Hadley Billington）领导下的“[[1988-1989年管理和计划委员会|1988-1989年管理和计划委员会]]”（1988–89 Management and Planning Committee）的努力下，《美国国会图书馆公报》问世<ref>{{cite book|title=Party Animals Travel Across the Nation: LC Traveling Exhibition Features Political Symbols|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1F1NAQAAMAAJ|year=1992|publisher=The Library|pages=9–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801204116/https://books.google.com/books?id=1F1NAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1990年4月6日，该报出版发行第一期<ref>{{cite book|title=Library of Congress Information Bulletin|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=x9YLxX2pn5wC|year=1992|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|pages=9–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801204115/https://books.google.com/books?id=x9YLxX2pn5wC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

